it turns out grandpa's really sick.

18:18.990 --> 18:20.710
But he's gonna get better,right?

18:22.660 --> 18:23.970
Come here.

18:27.450 --> 18:29.750
Sometimes people get so sick

18:29.960 --> 18:31.910
that they can't get better.

18:33.830 --> 18:35.840
