21:18.420 --> 21:20.690
It's gonna be okay,peyton.

21:20.800 --> 21:22.450
You think so?

21:22.570 --> 21:23.900
'Cause I'm kind of nervous.

21:24.030 --> 21:25.360
You're gonna do great.

